{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM07_140.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1c,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "...I'm going to tell you about the past. About myself, and Luard."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "...Luard was an exceedingly skilled alchemist. He was also a fellow researcher of alchemy alongside me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x6c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "He wasn't originally the way you just saw him... However, at one point, he began walking the wrong path."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Luard was taken in by the power of alchemy. His research became more and more self-righteous, and selfish."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I tried to convince him to stop... But he wouldn't listen to me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "In fact, he began to immerse himself in his alchemy research even further."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "If allowed to continue, his research could have affected the entire world... That's why I fought to stop him."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I killed him with my own hands, and split his soul into two artificial lifeforms."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "However, there was one thing that concerned me. The \"Cauldron of Knowledge\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Artificial lifeforms can't use alchemy. But the Cauldron is an exception."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "As long as the Cauldron existed, there was the possibility of Luard returning to his former self."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "That's why I sealed my own soul in that book."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I could change hands between alchemists, gaining new knowledge to prepare for the future."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x5,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "unknown2": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "However, over the long years, my memories were lost. And you know the rest of the story, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x24,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Something like that happened...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...Yes. Allowing Luard to resurrect himself was my failure."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "If Luard is allowed to go free, he will likely resume his alchemy research."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "And if he continues, something terrible could happen once again. That must be prevented at all costs."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "In order to do that, we need to figure out where Luard fled to."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Hmm... Where would he have gone?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "...I have no idea. Actually, I suppose it would be more correct to say that I can't remember."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It's likely that I already know where he would have gone. But I can't remember where."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I see... Oh, maybe..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Maybe if we keep bringing back your memories like before, you'll remember where he would go?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Yes, that seems very possible. However, we don't have much time to go about it leisurely."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I'll do what I can to investigate where Luard went. You continue improving your alchemy skills, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "That will likely be the quickest way of finding where he went."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x40,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I understand! Leave that to me, Plachta!"
        }
    ]
}